# stage 2 — cli + driver.
#
# This module is the apex of the compiler pipeline: it orchestrates
# every stage beneath it (lex → parse → resolve → infer → monomorph →
# perceus → emit) plus the CLI surface, core loading, builtin-effect
# injection, module-import resolution, the library-query mode, the
# AST/token/diagnostic dumpers, and the `compile_source`/`run` drivers.
#
# It imports modules, not bodies. Its public surface is just `run` +
# `parse_cli` — the two entry points `fn main()` in main.kai calls.
# Everything else is module-internal.

